Ukrainian Vyshivanka / Вишиванка - by EDG

Listen, and listen well.

I know that a certain part of the world is a war right now. I know that many of you are, have, or will possibly face death, and that it makes you afraid and angry.

I'm not in your head, and frankly I don't care.

I made this model to make a friend happy. Someone that had to deal with death and that needed to get cheered up. And I will cheer up my friend. You can't stop me.

I swear that if you (Russians, Ukrainians or other) use this comment section for politics, I will screencap each and every one of you that started shit and send that to the admins of the site.

This is meant to cheer up a friend who lost someone, NOT to start another conflict.

Please enjoy the clothing!
